{
  "stem": "26142.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Chani was-- was walking already with her mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my brother, Tsvi and I, we went-- we had to walk a few kilometers, maybe two kilometers-- and-- to the Dniester River, to where he had anchored his-- his-- his boat.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when we got closer, really, the roar, the water, the roar was-- was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is a wild, ferocious river.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when we got there, when I took a look at this little boat, I thought, oh my God.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Here we are, six people-- the guy-- seven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and-- and this whole boat is-- it's-- is-- is-- is the-- the size of a big-- big--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If we would have seen that boat, that so-called boat, we would have never gotten into it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no way back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got into that boat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the guy started navigating that boat, and-- and cutting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the-- the stream was so strong that it pulled us down, down, down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe it didn't take more than 10 minutes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe-- maybe it didn't take more than 10 minutes, but it was an eternity till we-- we finally got across the Dniester River-- across.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the way they-- they told us, exactly that's the way we went.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He-- he right away turned around and-- and-- and got us-- went back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we-- it was pitch dark-- pitch dark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We couldn't-- but once we got on the highway, fortunately, we didn't see a soul.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We walked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was only a half a kilometer, he told us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then on the right side, all of a sudden, the-- the-- the three white buildings appeared.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I started running-- to that-- to-- to the building when-- when-- as-- when as the building came in-- in-- in view.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
